  },
  {
    title: "5. Data Security",
    content:
      "We implement industry-standard security measures, including encryption, firewalls, and access controls, to protect your data. However, no method of data transmission is 100% secure, and we encourage users to follow best security practices.",
  },
  {
    title: "6. Your Rights",
    content:
      "You have the right to:\n\n- Access, update, or correct your personal information.\n- Request the deletion of your data (subject to legal and regulatory obligations).\n- Opt out of marketing communications.\n- Restrict or object to data processing in certain circumstances.",
  },
  {
    title: "7. Data Retention",
    content:
      "We retain your data for as long as necessary to fulfill our legal and operational requirements. Typically, financial transaction records must be stored for a minimum period as required by financial regulations.",
  },
  {
    title: "8. Cookies & Tracking Technologies",
    content:
      "Our website uses cookies to enhance user experience and collect analytics. You can manage or disable cookies through your browser settings, but doing so may affect site functionality.",
  },
  {
    title: "9. Policy Updates",
    content:
      "We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and significant updates may be communicated via email or platform notifications.",
  },
